SuperAdmin:
{
  "creator" :  null,
  "delegable": true,
  "effect": "allow", // deny - default:allow
  "action": "*", // not_action
  "resouce": "*",
  "condition": []
}

Everyone (implicit):
{
  "action": "*",
  "resource": "*",
  "condition": "creator == self"
}

Permission to add locations under location with id 7:
{
  "action": "locations#*",
  "resource": "cdp:location/5/7/*"
}

Create a device in any lab of institution 1:
{
  "action": "devices#create",
  "resource": [
    "cdp:laboratory/*",
    "cdp:institution/1"
  ]
}

Admin for devices under location 7:
{
  "action": "devices#*",
  "resource": [
    "cdp:institution/1",
    "cdp:laboratory/*",
    "cdp:location/5/7/*"
  ]
}

Admin for devices under location 7 (option B):
{
  "action": "*",
  "resource": "cdp:device",
  "condition" : [
    "cdp:institution == 1",
    "cdp:location == 5/7/*"
  ]
}

Institution Admin under location 7:
Statements: [
  {
    "action" : "*",
    "resource" : "cdp:laboratory/*",
    "condition": [
      "cdp:institution == 1",
      "cdp:location == 5/7/*"
    ]
  },
  {
    "action" : "*",
    "resource" : "cdp:device/*",
    "condition": "cdp:institution == 1"
  }
]

Institution Admin under location 7 (option B):
{
  "action" : [
    "device#list",
